id: pm-github-sq5l
title: Adopt current pm SDK and TypeScript 7 toolchain
description: "Consolidate the five overlapping pm-github dependency updates, synchronize package and manifest compatibility contracts, keep npm build artifacts out of Git, and validate every GitHub importer/exporter/search/hook registration against pm CLI 2026.7.10."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[5]: dependencies,github,release-readiness,sdk,toolchain
