author: codex
estimated_minutes: 60
acceptance_criteria: "pm CLI SDK/changelog, TypeScript, Node types, and checkout action are current; package peer/dev and manifest minimums agree on 2026.7.10; generated dist is published but untracked; full release and real installed-extension gates pass with zero vulnerabilities and no private data."
definition_of_ready: Current origin/main contains Dependabot configuration and the five update PRs are independently green.
reviewer: greptile
risk: medium
confidence: high
sprint: 2026-07-production
release: next
resolution: "Consolidated current dependency updates, synchronized pm 2026.7.10 peer/dev/manifest contracts, migrated importer/exporter help metadata to the SDK-native registration options, removed invalid manifest capability and duplicate explicit commands, updated checkout v7, and untracked generated dist."
expected_result: "Latest pm-github activates every intended command, field, importer, exporter, search provider, hook, and preflight without SDK capability or handler-collision warnings."
actual_result: "TypeScript 7 build and all 52 tests pass; zero production vulnerabilities; isolated latest-pm package doctor reports zero warnings with 5 commands, 36 flags, 6 item fields, 1 importer, 1 exporter, 1 search provider, 1 after-command hook, and 1 preflight; github help exposes import/export/sync/validate."
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-11T00:37:41.109Z",codex,registerImporter and registerExporter accept first-class command metadata in the current SDK; duplicating the derived commands causes self-collisions and loses the clean native integration contract.
